-$$
-
-即
-
-$$
-\frac {\mathrm{d} ^ {2} y}{\mathrm{d} t ^ {2}} - 2 \frac {\mathrm{d} y}{\mathrm{d} t} + y = \mathrm{e} ^ {t} + \mathrm{e} ^ {- t}.
-$$
